            <thetext>On the last Aristo release, on the appearance line 1886, there is a bug in function tabview-page/button/close-button, the image does not exist, so the close button on page tabView does not appear, here is a sample wich correct the problem :

   &quot;tabview-page/button/close-button&quot; :
   {
     alias : &quot;atom&quot;,
     style : function(states)
     {
       return {
         icon : &quot;aristo/decoration/window/close-inactive.png&quot;
       };
     }
   },</thetext>
